WEBVTT

00:02.633 --> 00:03.700
Hold up.

00:03.766 --> 00:07.700
Conservative suit,
zero‐cleavage factor.

00:07.766 --> 00:10.566
You droppin' that tired brother
Teddy tonight, huh?

00:10.633 --> 00:11.566
[scoffs]

00:11.633 --> 00:13.066
I'll give you a 7.2

00:13.133 --> 00:15.400
on the "All up
in my business" scale.

00:16.533 --> 00:17.866
[doorbell rings]

00:17.933 --> 00:21.166
Oh, that's my cue
to be up out of here.

00:21.233 --> 00:23.733
See, I don't wanna be here
when he starts making you guess

00:23.800 --> 00:26.300
how many green lights
he made on the way over.

00:26.366 --> 00:27.300
[scoffs]

00:28.333 --> 00:30.033
Hey, Teddy.

00:30.100 --> 00:31.733
Guess where I found
a parking space?

00:31.800 --> 00:32.966
Come on, guess.

00:33.033 --> 00:36.533
Okay, across the street
and three spaces down.

00:36.600 --> 00:40.466
Now, last time, it was across
the street and three spaces up.

00:40.533 --> 00:42.800
Spooky, huh?

00:46.466 --> 00:48.166
Yeah, I got a chill.

00:48.233 --> 00:50.633
Listen, um, Teddy, come on now,
we need, uh, have a seat.

00:50.700 --> 00:52.100
I think we need to talk..

00:53.366 --> 00:56.500
Now, I need a favor,
'cause my little sister, Marissa

00:56.566 --> 00:57.900
well, her boyfriend
just broke up with her

00:57.966 --> 01:00.773
and, well, she needs
a woman's point of view.

01:00.840 --> 01:02.506
Alright, well,
tell her to call me.

01:02.573 --> 01:04.506
Phones are so impersonal.

01:07.173 --> 01:08.773
Come on, girl.

01:11.406 --> 01:16.173
Marissa, this is
my lady friend Khadijah.

01:16.240 --> 01:17.606
‐ Hi.
‐ She got somethin' to tell ya.

01:17.673 --> 01:19.040
Hey, Marissa.

01:19.106 --> 01:22.973
So, uh, your boyfriend decided
he needed some air, huh?

01:23.040 --> 01:24.640
I hate him.

01:26.840 --> 01:29.240
Alright, now, just hold up now.

01:29.306 --> 01:32.573
I know‐I know you're hurtin',
but then don't take it personal.

01:34.740 --> 01:37.806
Listen, the important thing is
not to blame the other person.

01:37.873 --> 01:38.873
‐ Oh.
‐ I mean, think about it.

01:38.940 --> 01:40.240
He just made room
for the right guy

01:40.306 --> 01:42.240
to come into your life.

01:43.606 --> 01:47.273
Well, you know, I‐I never
thought about it like that.

01:47.340 --> 01:48.806
Well, you should.

01:48.873 --> 01:50.640
Shoot, everybody should.

01:51.940 --> 01:53.706
See, Marissa,
now gettin' dumped

01:53.773 --> 01:55.406
is not the end of the world.

01:55.473 --> 01:58.040
Sometimes it's the best thing
that can happen to ya.

01:58.106 --> 01:59.373
Exactly.

